-roll angle is a measure of the rotation of the UAV around its longitudinal axis;
-IMU (Inertial Measurement Unit) is a device that measures the acceleration and orientation of the UAV;
-Highest average roll angle implies the UAV that has the most extreme rotation around its longitudinal axis on average.

sql:
SELECT model, COUNT(*) as NumberOfUAVs
FROM uavs
GROUP BY model;
